    "description": "Ascend to the Earth's Surface and take back what's yours! <br><br>Inspired by vertical shmups like ZeroRanger and first-person shooters like Doom Eternal, Ascended Survivor delivers intense combat with action-packed music and deep lore. <br><br>    <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1821220/extras/a72c1fb39a7b48e74cdfef9afe1d7a60.poster.avif?t=1685122470\" width=306 height=544 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1821220/extras/a72c1fb39a7b48e74cdfef9afe1d7a60.webm?t=1685122470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1821220/extras/a72c1fb39a7b48e74cdfef9afe1d7a60.mp4?t=1685122470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You play as the Survivor, a human trapped at the center of the Earth. Your memories of your life on the surface are a jumbled haze. All you know is that you had a beautiful life on the surface and that it was all taken away from you. With your mangled body and the prototype DMS-0 mining ship, you'll tear apart anything that gets in the way of your quest to get your home back! <br><br>    <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1821220/extras/c9539e447ab036532d9db10bb28d484d.poster.avif?t=1685122470\" width=306 height=544 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1821220/extras/c9539e447ab036532d9db10bb28d484d.webm?t=1685122470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1821220/extras/c9539e447ab036532d9db10bb28d484d.mp4?t=1685122470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Ascended Survivor plays like the shmups you know and love, with the addition of a close-range melee attack. Add in special abilities, and you got a unique combat system that combines the perspective of vertical arcade shooters and the mechanics of character action games. <br><br>Each episode of Ascended Survivor takes place in a new layer of the planet, with striking environments and unique enemies and bosses. incredible design awaits around every level! <br><br>    <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1821220/extras/a4f2db81ccb8d73330596997aa2d9daf.poster.avif?t=1685122470\" width=306 height=544 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1821220/extras/a4f2db81ccb8d73330596997aa2d9daf.webm?t=1685122470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1821220/extras/a4f2db81ccb8d73330596997aa2d9daf.mp4?t=1685122470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
